item.title: FullCalendar'ı kullanmaya başlama
item.description: FullCalendar’ı İndirme # FullCalendar, web sitesinden indirilebilir: https://fullcalendar.io/download/ NPM adresinden: $ npm fullcalendar’ı kurun Bower adresinden: $ bower fullcalendar yükleyin veya CDNJS: //cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/fullcalendar/3.0.1/fullcalendar.min.js //cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/fullcalendar/3.0.1/fullcalendar.min.css //cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/fullcalendar/3.0.1/fullcalendar.print.css
